# ============================================
# Ignore everything, whitelist fz ecosystem only
# ============================================

# Ignore all by default
*

# --- fz ecosystem whitelist ---

# Skills
!skills/
!skills/*/
!skills/**/SKILL.md
!skills/**/references/
!skills/**/references/**
# Exclude heavy build artifacts inside skills
skills/**/references/.venv/
skills/**/references/__pycache__/
skills/**/references/uv.lock

# Agents
!agents/
!agents/*.md

# Modules
!modules/
!modules/*.md
!modules/patterns/
!modules/patterns/*.md

# Guides
!guides/
!guides/*.md

# Templates
!templates/
!templates/*.md

# Repo files
!.gitignore
!README.md
!RELEASE_NOTES_*.md
